          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price is from the year 2023. The price is estimated as a proxy based on the source: https://ag.purdue.edu/commercialag/home/resource/2023/03/indiana-farm-custom-rates/. The prices were adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
        </property>
        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Up to 2019, in the US, it is estimated that around 127 million acres have been treated with aerial application. Source: https://agairupdate.com/2021/08/02/a-century-of-agricultural-aviation-1921-2021/</productionVolumeComment>
