    <modellingAndValidation>
      <representativeness systemModelId="290c1f85-4cc4-4fa1-b0c8-2cb7f4276dce">
        <systemModelName xml:lang="en">Allocation, cut-off by classification</systemModelName>
        <samplingProcedure xml:lang="en">Average calculation based on 4 different agricultural aircrafts (Moraes, T.R., Cornago Junior, V.M., De Araújo, V.C., Esperancini, M.S. and Antuniassi, U.R., 2021. COST OF AERIAL AND GROUND SPRAYINGS AND TECHNOLOGICAL REPLACEMENT POINT: A CASE STUDY IN THE REGION OF MINEIROS, GO, BRAZIL. Engenharia Agrícola, 41, pp.359-367.) &amp; 171.6 l/hour average consumption of kerosene, 160ha/hour based on (Moraes, T.R., Cornago Junior, V.M., De Araújo, V.C., Esperancini, M.S. and Antuniassi, U.R., 2021. COST OF AERIAL AND GROUND SPRAYINGS AND TECHNOLOGICAL REPLACEMENT POINT: A CASE STUDY IN THE REGION OF MINEIROS, GO, BRAZIL. Engenharia Agrícola, 41, pp.359-367.) and (Albaugh, T.J., Vance, E.D., Gaudreault, C., Fox, T.R., Allen, H.L., Stape, J.L. and Rubilar, R.A., 2012. Carbon emissions and sequestration from fertilization of pine in the southeastern United States. Forest Science, 58(5), pp.419-429.)."</samplingProcedure>
        <extrapolations xml:lang="en">The dataset is modeled for agricultural production system in US. Data Quality indicators are adjusted accordingly. Scaled for 0,877 kg of input of kasorese based on the transport, passenger aircraft, very short haul. GLO</extrapolations>
      </representativeness>
